        public TDConfig setMutiprocess​(boolean isSupportMultiProcess)

        public static TDConfig getInstance​(android.content.Context context,
                                   java.lang.String token,
                                   java.lang.String url)
        Obtain the TDConfig instance. This example can be used to initialize ThinkingAnalyticsSDK. Each SDK instance corresponds to one TDConfig instance.
        参数:
        context - app context
        token - APP ID
        url - The URL of the data receiving end must be the complete URL with the protocol; otherwise, an exception will be thrown
        返回:
        TDConfig instance
